textAfterTable: 12 Songs Biography Genre: Pop Years Active: Discovered during a stopover in Brussels while working as an entertainer on a North European cruise ship, Belgian Bart Herman spent the next two decades balancing his music career with ventures into both TV and theater. Fusing classic rock & roll with Tex-Mex, Latin pop, and easy listening, he scored his first hit in 1993 with "Ik Ga Dood Aan Jou" and achieved his highest-charting album eight years later with Verzameld (No.4).
